title: Houses of the World
description:
Title: Houses of the World
Author: Francisco Asensio Cerver
File Extension: .djvu


Photographs of houses from various locations, interior and exterior shots. This book focuses on the modern/contemporary/minimalist style. It is divided up into the following sections: "Houses in the City", "Houses in the Suburbs", "Houses by the Sea", "Houses in the Country", and "Houses in the Mountains."
